WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.000
We received a lot of feedback from
customers about unnecessary

00:00:04.025 --> 00:00:05.200
clicking in training modules.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.100
So we chose to use high quality
videos to deliver concise

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:13.040
content in a fun, engaging, 
and creative way.

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:18.420
In addition, videos allow us to
implement closed captioning

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:23.940
and adhere to the web content
accessibility guidelines (WCAG).

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.200
This is a universal set of accessibility
standards that allows all areas of

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:31.200
information and communication
technology (ICT)

00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:34.000
to communicate with web sites.